Export up to 50,000 rows from a Data Cloud report using the .csv, .xls, or .xlsx file formats. This limit includes totals and subtotals. Previously, the limit was 2,000 rows.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

How: From the Reports tab or from the report run page, click and select Export.
title: Enhanced Data Cloud Report Export
